## üßë‚Äçüíª How to use:
1Ô∏è‚É£ Clone the Repository:</br>
```sh
git clone https://github.com/AnshMNSoni/PyShell.git
```

2Ô∏è‚É£ Install all require dependencies:</br>
```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3Ô∏è‚É£ SignUp to Open Weather For weather API: [Visit](https://openweathermap.org/)

4Ô∏è‚É£ Replace you API_KEY:
- Inside `get_weather` function
- api_key = "YOUR_API_KEY" </br>

###### Preview</br></br>
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b6928f38-0319-48ba-aaaf-39d1f7b873e7)
</br>

5Ô∏è‚É£ Lastly, Open you terminal and run:</br>
```sh
python main.py
```

